            "url": "https://www.jujubemonster.com/the-stage-is-set.html",
            "title": "The Stage Is Set",
            "summary": "The stage is set. Afternoon creeps in, settling into the velvet, waiting for the weight of the hour to unravel, petal by petal. The patchwork of calico and cream lies undisturbed in a slow, rhythmic rise and fall. Dust, shadow, silence— just soft things to&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">The stage is set.</p>\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Afternoon creeps in,<br>settling into the velvet,<br>waiting for the weight of the hour <br>to unravel,<br>petal by petal.</p>\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">The patchwork of calico and cream<br>lies undisturbed in a slow, rhythmic rise and fall.<br>Dust, shadow, silence— <br>just soft things to curl into.</p>\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Nothing argues my nap here.</p>\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">–jujube</p>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-2801\" src=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/catsleep.jpeg?w=1024\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/catsleep.jpeg?w=1024 1024w, https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/catsleep.jpeg?w=2048 2048w, https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/catsleep.jpeg?w=150 150w, https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/catsleep.jpeg?w=300 300w, https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/catsleep.jpeg?w=768 768w, https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/catsleep.jpeg?w=1440 1440w\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"771\" data-attachment-id=\"2801\" data-permalink=\"https://unusualcolors.com/2026/03/29/the-stage-is-set/catsleep/\" data-orig-file=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/catsleep.jpeg\" data-orig-size=\"3000,2260\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;f0d78709-0544-4b6c-90e4-75c59c7c4d40&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;Signature: &quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"catsleep\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"&lt;p&gt;Signature: &lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-large-file=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/catsleep.jpeg?w=960\"></figure>",
