            "id": "https://www.jujubemonster.com/pigments-of-time.html",
            "url": "https://www.jujubemonster.com/pigments-of-time.html",
            "title": "Pigments of Time",
            "summary": "Pigments of time blots and blooms into the canvas of dawn. The tiered eaves of the ancient pagoda sign off the night with the waking ray Mist drifts apart like a half-whispered morning greeting forever deferred in the bleed of light. –Jujube",
            "content_html": "<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Pigments of time<br>blots and blooms<br>into the canvas of dawn.<br>The tiered eaves of the ancient pagoda<br>sign off the night with the waking ray<br>Mist drifts apart<br>like a half-whispered morning greeting<br>forever deferred in the bleed of light.</p>\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">–Jujube</p>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><figure class=\"wp-image-2797\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/morningbj.png?w=720\" sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\" srcset=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/morningbj.png 720w, https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/morningbj.png?w=113 113w, https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/morningbj.png?w=226 226w\" alt=\"\" width=\"720\" height=\"956\" data-attachment-id=\"2797\" data-permalink=\"https://unusualcolors.com/2026/03/22/pigments-of-time/morningbj/\" data-orig-file=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/morningbj.png\" data-orig-size=\"720,956\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"morningbj\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/morningbj.png?w=720\"></figure></figure>",
