        {
            "id": "https://www.jujubemonster.com/a-winter-tree.html",
            "url": "https://www.jujubemonster.com/a-winter-tree.html",
            "title": "A Winter Tree",
            "summary": "Tangled vines, like frayed harp-strings, enact a wayward joy. Worldlings have turned away, hidden indoors to nurse their fire. But the trunk bends into a question mark between frost and rust, challenging all the assumptions of the season. –Jujube",
            "content_html": "<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Tangled vines,<br>like frayed harp-strings,<br>enact a wayward joy.<br>Worldlings have turned away,<br>hidden indoors to nurse their fire.<br>But the trunk bends <br>into a question mark<br>between frost and rust,<br>challenging all the assumptions of the season. </p>\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">–Jujube</p>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><figure class=\"wp-image-2790\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/abstracttree.png?w=864\" sizes=\"(max-width: 864px) 100vw, 864px\" srcset=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/abstracttree.png 864w, https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/abstracttree.png?w=150 150w, https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/abstracttree.png?w=300 300w, https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/abstracttree.png?w=768 768w\" alt=\"\" width=\"864\" height=\"864\" data-attachment-id=\"2790\" data-permalink=\"https://unusualcolors.com/2026/03/15/a-winter-tree/abstracttree/\" data-orig-file=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/abstracttree.png\" data-orig-size=\"864,864\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"abstracttree\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/abstracttree.png?w=864\"></figure></figure>",
