        {
            "id": "https://www.jujubemonster.com/stopping-by-woods-on-a-snowy-evening.html",
            "url": "https://www.jujubemonster.com/stopping-by-woods-on-a-snowy-evening.html",
            "title": "Stopping by Woods on a Snowy Evening",
            "summary": "The only other sound’s the sweep Of easy wind and downy flake. The woods are lovely, dark and deep, But I have promises to keep, And miles to go before I sleep, And miles to go before I sleep. — Robert Frost",
            "content_html": "<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">The only other sound’s the sweep   <br>Of easy wind and downy flake.   </p>\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">The woods are lovely, dark and deep,   <br>But I have promises to keep,   <br>And miles to go before I sleep,   <br>And miles to go before I sleep.</p>\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">— Robert Frost</p>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-resized\"><figure class=\"wp-image-2785\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/walk1.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 648px) 100vw, 648px\" srcset=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/walk1.png 648w, https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/walk1.png?w=113&amp;h=150 113w, https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/walk1.png?w=226&amp;h=300 226w\" alt=\"\" width=\"648\" height=\"860\" data-attachment-id=\"2785\" data-permalink=\"https://unusualcolors.com/2026/03/08/stopping-by-woods-on-a-snowy-evening/walk1/\" data-orig-file=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/walk1.png\" data-orig-size=\"648,860\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"walk1\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/walk1.png?w=648\"></figure></figure>",
            "image": "https://www.jujubemonster.com/media/posts/92/walk1.png",
            "author": {
                "name": "Jujube"
            },
            "tags": [
                   "travel",
                   "poetry",
