        {
            "id": "https://www.jujubemonster.com/prism.html",
            "url": "https://www.jujubemonster.com/prism.html",
            "title": "Prism",
            "summary": "Where the light fractures, no shadow, past or present, can hide you. Time, pinned in space: does it lift what you carry, or anchor it forever? Amid the silent roar, going, yet never gone, you stand, trying to finish the sentence. — Jujube",
            "content_html": "<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Where the light fractures,<br>no shadow, past or present,<br>can hide you.</p>\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Time, pinned in space:<br>does it lift what you carry,<br>or anchor it forever?</p>\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Amid the silent roar,<br>going, yet never gone,<br>you stand,<br>trying to finish the sentence.</p>\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">— Jujube</p>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-resized\"><figure class=\"wp-image-2778\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/existence.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 792px) 100vw, 792px\" srcset=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/existence.png 792w, https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/existence.png?w=109&amp;h=150 109w, https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/existence.png?w=219&amp;h=300 219w, https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/existence.png?w=768&amp;h=1052 768w\" alt=\"\" width=\"792\" height=\"1085\" data-attachment-id=\"2778\" data-permalink=\"https://unusualcolors.com/2026/03/01/prism/existence/\" data-orig-file=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/existence.png\" data-orig-size=\"792,1085\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"existence\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/existence.png?w=747\"></figure></figure>",
            "image": "https://www.jujubemonster.com/media/posts/91/existence.png",
            "author": {
