        {
            "id": "https://www.jujubemonster.com/visiting-the-sky-mother-mountain-in-a-dream-a-song-of-farewell.html",
            "url": "https://www.jujubemonster.com/visiting-the-sky-mother-mountain-in-a-dream-a-song-of-farewell.html",
            "title": "Visiting the Sky-Mother Mountain in a Dream: A Song of Farewell",
            "summary": "脚著谢公屐， 身登青云梯。 半壁见海日， 空中闻天鸡。 … 列缺霹雳， 丘峦崩摧。 洞天石扉， 訇然中开。 Wearing the climbing shoes of Lord Xie, I ascend the ladder of blue clouds. Halfway up, I see the sun rising from the sea, In mid-air, I hear the rooster of heaven crow. … Lightning flashes&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">脚著谢公屐，<br>身登青云梯。<br>半壁见海日，<br>空中闻天鸡。<br>…<br>列缺霹雳，<br>丘峦崩摧。<br>洞天石扉，<br>訇然中开。</p>\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><em>Wearing the climbing shoes of Lord Xie,</em><br><em>I ascend the ladder of blue clouds.</em><br><em>Halfway up, I see the sun rising from the sea,</em><br><em>In mid-air, I hear the rooster of heaven crow.</em><br><em>…</em><br><em>Lightning flashes and thunder roars,</em><br><em>The peaks and ridges crumble and break.</em><br><em>The stone gate of the cavernous heaven,</em><br><em>Thunders open to reveal the sky.</em></p>\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">— Li Bai 李白 (701-762)</p>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-resized\"><figure class=\"wp-image-2773\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/path.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 648px) 100vw, 648px\" srcset=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/path.png 648w, https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/path.png?w=113&amp;h=150 113w, https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/path.png?w=226&amp;h=300 226w\" alt=\"\" width=\"648\" height=\"860\" data-attachment-id=\"2773\" data-permalink=\"https://unusualcolors.com/2026/02/22/visiting-the-sky-mother-mountain-in-a-dream-a-song-of-farewell/path/\" data-orig-file=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/path.png\" data-orig-size=\"648,860\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"path\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/path.png?w=648\"></figure></figure>",
            "image": "https://www.jujubemonster.com/media/posts/90/path.png",
            "author": {
                "name": "Jujube"
            },
            "tags": [
                   "poetry",
                   "nature",
                   "Chinese poems"
            ],
            "date_published": "2026-02-22T12:33:00-08:00",
            "date_modified": "2026-07-19T12:33:59-07:00"
        },
        {
            "id": "https://www.jujubemonster.com/my-princess.html",
            "url": "https://www.jujubemonster.com/my-princess.html",
            "title": "My Princess",
            "summary": "My small, preserved princess, you cradle yesterday’s snow and last night’s shadow, each a parenthesis in fur around your perfect refusal. How delicately you decline the invitation to wake and play the part assigned. The nursery clock has stopped at forever, and still, you will not&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">My small, preserved princess,<br>you cradle yesterday’s snow<br>and last night’s shadow,<br>each a parenthesis in fur <br>around your perfect refusal.</p>\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">How delicately you decline <br>the invitation to wake<br>and play the part assigned.<br>The nursery clock has stopped at<em> forever</em>,<br>and still, you will not blink.</p>\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">— Jujube</p>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-resized\"><figure class=\"wp-image-2767\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/bwdolls.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\" srcset=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/bwdolls.png 720w, https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/bwdolls.png?w=113&amp;h=150 113w, https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/bwdolls.png?w=226&amp;h=300 226w\" alt=\"\" width=\"720\" height=\"956\" data-attachment-id=\"2767\" data-permalink=\"https://unusualcolors.com/2026/02/15/my-princess/bwdolls/\" data-orig-file=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/bwdolls.png\" data-orig-size=\"720,956\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"bwdolls\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/bwdolls.png?w=720\"></figure></figure>",
