        {
            "id": "https://www.jujubemonster.com/the-darkling-thrush.html",
            "url": "https://www.jujubemonster.com/the-darkling-thrush.html",
            "title": "The Darkling Thrush",
            "summary": "I leant upon a coppice gate When Frost was spectre-grey, And Winter’s dregs made desolate The weakening eye of day. The tangled bine-stems scored the sky Like strings of broken lyres, And all mankind that haunted nigh Had sought their household fires. — Thomas Hardy",
            "content_html": "<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">I leant upon a coppice gate<br>When Frost was spectre-grey,<br>And Winter’s dregs made desolate<br>The weakening eye of day.<br>The tangled bine-stems scored the sky<br>Like strings of broken lyres,<br>And all mankind that haunted nigh<br>Had sought their household fires.</p>\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">— Thomas Hardy</p>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-resized\"><figure class=\"wp-image-2762\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/wintersnow.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 792px) 100vw, 792px\" srcset=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/wintersnow.png 792w, https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/wintersnow.png?w=113&amp;h=150 113w, https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/wintersnow.png?w=226&amp;h=300 226w, https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/wintersnow.png?w=768&amp;h=1019 768w\" alt=\"\" width=\"792\" height=\"1051\" data-attachment-id=\"2762\" data-permalink=\"https://unusualcolors.com/2026/02/08/the-darkling-thrush/wintersnow/\" data-orig-file=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/wintersnow.png\" data-orig-size=\"792,1051\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"wintersnow\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/wintersnow.png?w=772\"></figure></figure>",
            "image": "https://www.jujubemonster.com/media/posts/88/wintersnow.png",
            "author": {
                "name": "Jujube"
