        {
            "id": "https://www.jujubemonster.com/autumn-words.html",
            "url": "https://www.jujubemonster.com/autumn-words.html",
            "title": "Autumn Words",
            "summary": "晴空一鹤排云上， 便引诗情到碧霄。 A crane soars above the clouds and soars high, Lifts my poetic heart up to the azure sky. — Liu Yuxi 刘禹锡 (772-842)",
            "content_html": "<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">晴空一鹤排云上，<br>便引诗情到碧霄。</p>\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">A crane soars above the clouds and soars high,<br>Lifts my poetic heart up to the azure sky.</p>\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">— Liu Yuxi 刘禹锡 (772-842)</p>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-resized\"><figure class=\"wp-image-2754\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/crane.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\" srcset=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/crane.png 720w, https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/crane.png?w=113&amp;h=150 113w, https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/crane.png?w=226&amp;h=300 226w\" alt=\"\" width=\"720\" height=\"956\" data-attachment-id=\"2754\" data-permalink=\"https://unusualcolors.com/2026/02/01/autumn-words/crane-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/crane.png\" data-orig-size=\"720,956\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"crane\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/crane.png?w=720\"></figure></figure>",
